  <brief_title>Incision and Drainage Versus Needle Aspiration in Soft Tissue Abscesses</brief_title>
  <official_title>Ultrasound Guided Needle Drainage Versus Formal Incision and Drainage of Superficial Soft Tissue Abscesses in the Emergency Department Setting</official_title>
